Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:16.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,500)}君と出會ったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:20.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,500)}ただの偶然じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:26.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,500)}これを運命と呼ぶんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:30.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,500)}その瞳に映る
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:34.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ぼくたちが輝いて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:38.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いられるようにずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:40.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見つめ續けて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:44.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1035)\fad(0,250)\blur3}Please be だからもしこの胸が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:49.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1035)\fad(250,0)\blur3}With me 道に迷う日には
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:54.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,500)}未來への扉を開いてほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:58.17,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ready, ready ready for the take off
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}未知なる世界へと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}舞い上がるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:09.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だからその手離さないで buddy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:12.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ready, ready ready for the take off
